      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily driver. While you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular use, the interior is clean and the body is in great shape. Overall, it is a solid, road-ready vehicle that offers a great balance of performance and value.",
