    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-maintained and still has plenty of life left for all your weekend adventures! If you're looking for a dependable car that looks great and runs even better, this is definitely the one for you. It's super clean and ready for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
