      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 987.2 Cayman S powered by the 3.4L MA1.21 direct-fuel-injection flat-six. This iteration eliminates the IMS bearing concerns of its predecessors, offering a linear, high-revving powerband. The 6-speed manual transaxle features crisp synchro engagement, delivering power to the rear wheels with exceptional tactile feedback. The mid-engine layout ensures a low polar moment of inertia, while the hydraulic steering rack offers a degree of communicative feedback absent in modern EPS units. Recent maintenance includes an Air-Oil Separator (AOS) replacement and a cooling system pressure test. The chassis remains taut with no significant bushing deflection, and the brake system has been refreshed with high-temp fluid to ensure consistent pedal feel. This is a driver-centric example optimized for peak lateral acceleration and throttle response.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Everything functions as intended.",
      "price": 29000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and style, perfect for someone who appreciates a well-cared-for machine. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful, deep gloss, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the interior is clean and inviting; the upholstery is free of tears, though there is some light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, including the premium sound system, heated seats, and navigation, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and provides smooth, consistent power. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, including a recent transmission fluid flush and a new set of all-season tires with plenty of tread remaining. The car has a clean title, has never been in an accident, and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. I am happy to provide the full service history to serious inquiries to demonstrate the care this car has received.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Meticulously maintained and presenting in superior mechanical order, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by both poise and reliability. Every aspect of this automobile reflects a commitment to quality, ensuring it remains a sophisticated and dependable asset for its next owner. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the exceptional standard of this offering.",
      "price": 34900.0,
