      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road. It runs smooth and has been well-cared for, so you can just hop in and go! Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin or have any questions. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
