      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a recently serviced VANOS system and updated rod bearings, ensuring peak performance up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to address chassis fatigue. The suspension remains taut with refreshed dampers and bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and lateral stability these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the drivetrain and structural integrity make this a premier driver-spec M3.",
